[*] --> Archived
Archived --> OnHold : submit
OnHold --> Rejected : reject
OnHold : entry / log staff
Rejected --> Created : reject
Created --> Pending : cancel
Created : entry / log staff
Created --> OnHold : revert
Pending --> [*]
